<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Food Delivery App</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .carousel-item img {
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            object-fit: cover; 
            filter: brightness(0.9);
        }

        .carousel-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03));
            z-index: 1; 
        }

        .carousel-caption {
            color: white; /* Set text color to white */
        }

        .carousel-caption h5,
        .carousel-caption p {
                color: white !important; /* Ensures all caption text is white */
         }

        .about-us, .how-to-order {
            padding-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            
        }

        .about-us {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
        }

        .how-to-order {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            
        }

        .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #f7c06d;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Carousel -->
    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="https://c4.wallpaperflare.com/wallpaper/633/800/36/food-burger-hd-wallpaper-preview.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Food Burger">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Delicious Burgers</h5>
                    <p>Enjoy our wide selection of juicy burgers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://c4.wallpaperflare.com/wallpaper/839/9/314/food-pizza-still-life-wallpaper-preview.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Food Pizza">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Fresh Pizza</h5>
                    <p>Try our freshly baked pizzas with a variety of toppings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://cdn.britannica.com/52/128652-050-14AD19CA/Maki-zushi.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Food Dish">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Exquisite Dishes</h5>
                    <p>Savor our gourmet dishes made with high-quality ingredients.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>


    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
          
            <div class="col-md-6 about-us">
                <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
                <p>Welcome to FoodDelivery, your premier destination for delicious food delivery. Our mission is to provide you with a seamless and enjoyable dining experience from the comfort of your home. We partner with top local restaurants to bring you a diverse selection of dishes, all delivered right to your doorstep.</p>
                <p>At FoodDelivery, we value quality, convenience, and customer satisfaction. Our easy-to-use platform allows you to browse menus, place orders, and track your delivery in real-time. Whether you're craving a hearty meal or a quick snack, we're here to make sure you get exactly what you want, fast and fresh.</p>
                <p>Thank you for choosingFoodDelivery. We look forward to serving you!</p>
            </div>

           
            <div class="col-md-6 how-to-order">
                <h2 class="section-title">How to Order</h2>
                <ol>
                   
                    <li>Register and login</li>
                    <li>Choose your restaurant</li>
                    <li>Select what you want to order and add to shopping cart</li>
                    <li>Insert delivery address and your phone number</li>
                    <li>Order and wait for the delivery guy</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
